{
  "description": "A breathtaking nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated with vibrant lights and a spectacular fireworks display. A long bridge with glowing white lights stretches across dark water, leading towards a cluster of tall buildings. The cityscape is a tapestry of golden and white lights, punctuated by a striking blue skyscraper. Fireworks explode in bursts of red, white, and blue above the city, creating a dynamic and festive atmosphere. In the background, rolling hills are visible, adding depth to the scene. The overall composition is dominated by the contrast between the dark water, the illuminated bridge and city, and the brilliant fireworks.",
